parameters:
Thief Nora: What an amazing building! Is this the number one
church in the empire?

Priestess Sophia: This is the place that oversees the Terios
Church. Normally, it is where the messengers of the Three
Goddesses, known as the priestesses, reside.
Clea: So, normally, are the priestesses not here right now?

Priestess Sophia: There is a pilgrimage ritual called the
Divine Crossing, and in the end, we offer prayers to the
main goddess, Sol, in front of this temple.

Priestess Sophia: This is the ritual that Agonia was talking
about.

Mage Relm: Sophia-san, when you speak seriously, it throws
me off balance.

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, even though I may not look like it,
I am a humble priestess of the Terios Church!
Clea: First, let's listen to what the client has to say.

Would you like to try again? ※ If you choose No, it will be
game over.
General Atu: Hahaha! My sword struck before your knife did!

Guild Leader Agonia: As expected, when you stay away from
the battlefield, your body becomes dull.
Clea: I let one escape. I apologize.

Guild Leader Agonia: I thought I had wiped them all out
before they got here... To think they would actually make it
this far.

Stolge of Affection: There were more of them than I
thought. I sensed some kind of movement, but I didn't expect
them to come this far.

General Atu: Pests naturally appear, and there may be bugs
that Clea attracted as well.

General Atu: The Dragon Slayer is a special existence. Clea,
who defeated the dragon, is their enemy, a symbol of demons.
Clea: Thank you for your advice.

Guild Leader Agonia: Eventually, a request to subjugate
demon worshippers might come our way.

Stolge of Affection: Well, Agonia and I will be heading
back. We're looking forward to hearing about your audience.

Clea: You were able to greet Mr. Laoco and the shrine
maiden, right?

Priestess Sophia: Sending General Atu here... means that
Caron's side is finally ready.
Thief Nora: Ah, we need to hurry too!

Mage Relm: Assuming we return to the guild in the end... are
there any other people who would be willing to cooperate?

Clea (Remember the days of adventure... There must be people
who will cooperate with us)
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

events.name: EV034アクティナの巫女からの依頼1-10

parameters:
Thief Nora: The reward was a bit disappointing, huh? I was
hoping for something delicious or useful!

Mage Relm: It's the secret underground ruins of the Atomis
Temple, right? It's amazing that even someone from the Magic
Academy like me can enter legally!

Priestess Sophia: I haven't heard any rumors about it. It
could be considered the Terios Church's biggest secret.
One-armed Opro: Why are you here...?

One-armed Opro: It's a stupid question. There's no way the
Dragon Slayer wouldn't be called by the priestess.
Clea: Opro-san, do you know the priestess?

One-armed Opro: I am called the Goblin Slayer, favored by
the priestess Actina, and I receive requests for monster
hunting.
Clea: So, that means this is also a request, right?

One-armed Opro: That seems to be the case... This time, it
looks like it's going to be a big game hunt after a long
time.

One-armed Opro: We may meet again somewhere on our journey,
take care.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
